  >
    <p class="max-w-3xl leading-8 text-[#4f4a45]">
      Launch copy should use source-backed With Connection biography material, including Katie's early childhood leadership, clinical background, publication history, and relationship-centered philosophy.
    </p>
  </Section>
  <InquiryCta />
</BaseLayout>
